title: Seamless Justifications - Research
text:
This website houses my undergraduate research on cognitive dissonance and consumer behavior. The research explores how learning about unethical manufacturing practices affects consumers’ evaluations of products they’ve already chosen.



The Effect of Negative Information on the Justification of Chosen Alternatives
[Second Project Title]
